title: Spittin' Chiclets Episode 312: Featuring Kirby Dach + James Duthie
description:
On Episode 312, the guys are joined by Kirby Dach and James Duthie. Kirby joined (32:33) the podcast for his second time to discuss being named Captain of Team Canada for the World Juniors, his rookie season, the bubble and more. The guys then talk some NHL news, including the new divisions, the return to play, some free agents and tons more. The boys are then joined by James Duthie (01:18:44) to talk about his new book, his career, 2021 World Juniors and everything in between.. The guys wrap up talking Tiger/Charlie Woods and some Soccer.


You can find every episode of this show on Apple Podcasts, Spotify or YouTube. Prime Members can listen ad-free on Amazon Music. For more, visit barstool.link/schiclets
